<p>He was born in 1989 in Istanbul. After graduating from Koç High School, he graduated from Koç University Electronics Engineering and completed his master's degree in Industrial Management at Purdue University in the USA. He is interested in family business and has investments in the field of Solar Energy. Akşehirlioğlu, who maintains his relations with civil society, is also a member of Ashoka ASN. In addition, he continues his postgraduate studies in the field of Sufism at Üsküdar University.</p>